quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  40,59,"Dájúdájú Àkókò náà ń bọ̀, kò sì sí iyèméjì nínú rẹ̀. Ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ àwọn ènìyàn ni kò gbàgbọ́.",""
  40,60,"Olúwa yín sọ pé: “Ẹ pè Mí, kí N̄g jẹ́pè yín. Dájúdájú àwọn tó ń ṣègbéraga nípa jíjọ́sìn fún Mi,<sup>1</sup> wọn yóò wọ inú iná Jahanamọ ní ẹni yẹpẹrẹ.”","[1] Ẹ wo sūrah Yūnus; 10:22 àti ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ rẹ̀."
  40,61,"Allāhu ni Ẹni tí Ó ṣe òru fún yín nítorí kí ẹ lè sinmi nínú rẹ̀. (Ó sì ṣe) ọ̀sán (nítorí kí ẹ lè fi) ríran. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Ọlọ́lá-jùlọ lórí àwọn ènìyàn, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ àwọn ènìyàn kì í dúpẹ́ (fún Un).",""
  40,62,"Ìyẹn ni Allāhu, Olúwa yín, Ẹlẹ́dàá gbogbo n̄ǹkan. Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Nítorí náà, báwo ni wọ́n ṣe ń ṣẹ yín lórí kúrò níbi òdodo?",""
  40,63,"Báyẹn náà ni wọ́n ṣe ń ṣẹ́ àwọn tó ń tako àwọn āyah Allāhu lórí kúrò níbi òdodo (ṣíwájú tiwọn).",""
  40,64,"Allāhu ni Ẹni tí Ó ṣe ilẹ̀ fún yín ní ibùgbé. Ó sì ṣe sánmọ̀ ní àjà (le yín lórí). Ó ya àwòrán yín. Ó sì ya àwòrán yín dáradára. Ó pèsè arísìkí fún yín nínú àwọn n̄ǹkan dáadáa. Ìyẹn ni Allāhu, Olúwa yín. Nítorí náà, mímọ́ ni fún Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.",""
  40,65,"Òun ni Alààyè. Kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí ẹ gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Nítorí náà, ẹ pè É lẹ́ni tí yóò máa fi àfọ̀mọ́-ọkàn (àníyàn mímọ́) ṣe ẹ̀sìn fún Un.<sup>1</sup> Gbogbo ẹyìn ń jẹ́ ti Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Al-’a‘rọ̄f; 7:29."
  40,66,"Sọ pé: “Dájúdájú Wọ́n kọ̀ fún mi pé kí n̄g jọ́sìn fún àwọn tí ẹ̀ ń pè lẹ́yìn Allāhu, nígbà tí àwọn ẹ̀rí tó yanjú ti dé bá mi láti ọ̀dọ̀ Olúwa mi, tí wọ́n sì pa mí ní àṣẹ pé kí n̄g juwọ́ jusẹ̀ sílẹ̀ (kí n̄g jẹ́ mùsùlùmí) fún Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.",""
